{"id":103,"ayahs":[{"number":155,"arabic":"فَبِمَا نَقْضِهِم مِّيثَٰقَهُمْ وَكُفْرِهِم بِـَٔايَٰتِ ٱللَّهِ وَقَتْلِهِمُ ٱلْأَنۢبِيَآءَ بِغَيْرِ حَقٍّۢ وَقَوْلِهِمْ قُلُوبُنَا غُلْفٌۢ ۚ بَلْ طَبَعَ ٱللَّهُ عَلَيْهَا بِكُفْرِهِمْ فَلَا يُؤْمِنُونَ إِلَّا قَلِيلًۭا","translation":"And so, [We punished them] for the break­ing of their pledge, and their refusal to acknowledge God's messages, and their slaying of prophets against all right, and their boast, \"Our hearts are already full of knowledge\"- nay, but God has sealed their hearts in result of their denial of the truth, and [now] they believe in but few things -;","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/648.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":81179,"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِمَا","translation":"অতঃপর কারণে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81180,"position":2,"arabic":"نَقْضِهِم","translation":"তাদের ভঙ্গের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81181,"position":3,"arabic":"مِّيثَـٰقَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের অঙ্গীকার","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81182,"position":4,"arabic":"وَكُفْرِهِم","translation":"ও তাদের অস্বীকার করার","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81183,"position":5,"arabic":"بِـَٔايَـٰتِ","translation":"আয়াতগুলোকে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81184,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81185,"position":7,"arabic":"وَقَتْلِهِمُ","translation":"ও তাদের হত্যা করার","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81186,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنۢبِيَآءَ","translation":"নবীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81187,"position":9,"arabic":"بِغَيْرِ","translation":"(অন্যভাবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81188,"position":10,"arabic":"حَقٍّۢ","translation":"অন্যায়ভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81189,"position":11,"arabic":"وَقَوْلِهِمْ","translation":"ও তাদের এ উক্তির (কারণে যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81190,"position":12,"arabic":"قُلُوبُنَا","translation":"''আমাদের অন্তরগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81191,"position":13,"arabic":"غُلْفٌۢ ۚ","translation":"আচ্ছাদিত (তারা অভিশপ্ত হয়)''","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81193,"position":14,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81194,"position":15,"arabic":"طَبَعَ","translation":"মোহর মেরে দিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81195,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81196,"position":17,"arabic":"عَلَيْهَا","translation":"তার উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81197,"position":18,"arabic":"بِكُفْرِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের কুফরীর কারণে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81198,"position":19,"arabic":"فَلَا","translation":"তাই না","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81199,"position":20,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"তারা ঈমান আনবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81200,"position":21,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"তবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81201,"position":22,"arabic":"قَلِيلًۭا","translation":"অল্পসংখ্যক","audioUrl":"wbw/004_155_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81202,"position":23,"arabic":"١٥٥","translation":"(১৫৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":156,"arabic":"وَبِكُفْرِهِمْ وَقَوْلِهِمْ عَلَىٰ مَرْيَمَ بُهْتَٰنًا عَظِيمًۭا","translation":"and for their refusal to acknowledge the truth, and the awesome calumny which they utter against Mary,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/649.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":81219,"position":1,"arabic":"وَبِكُفْرِهِمْ","translation":"এবং তাদের কুফরীর কারণে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_156_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81220,"position":2,"arabic":"وَقَوْلِهِمْ","translation":"এবং তাদের উক্তির (কারণেও)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_156_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81221,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_156_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81222,"position":4,"arabic":"مَرْيَمَ","translation":"মারইয়ামের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_156_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81223,"position":5,"arabic":"بُهْتَـٰنًا","translation":"(যা ছিল) অপবাদ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_156_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81224,"position":6,"arabic":"عَظِيمًۭا","translation":"গুরুতর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_156_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81225,"position":7,"arabic":"١٥٦","translation":"(১৫৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":157,"arabic":"وَقَوْلِهِمْ إِنَّا قَتَلْنَا ٱلْمَسِيحَ عِيسَى ٱبْنَ مَرْيَمَ رَسُولَ ٱللَّهِ وَمَا قَتَلُوهُ وَمَا صَلَبُوهُ وَلَٰكِن شُبِّهَ لَهُمْ ۚ وَإِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱخْتَلَفُوا۟ فِيهِ لَفِى شَكٍّۢ مِّنْهُ ۚ مَا لَهُم بِهِۦ مِنْ عِلْمٍ إِلَّا ٱتِّبَاعَ ٱلظَّنِّ ۚ وَمَا قَتَلُوهُ يَقِينًۢا","translation":"and their boast, \"Behold, we have slain the Christ Jesus, son of Mary, [who claimed to be] an apostle of God!\" However, they did not slay him, and neither did they crucify him, but it only seemed to them [as if it had been] so; and, verily, those who hold conflict­ing views thereon are indeed confused, having no [real] knowledge thereof, and following mere con­jecture. For, of a certainty, they did not slay him:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/650.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":81444,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَوْلِهِمْ","translation":"এবং তাদের উক্তি (এও যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81445,"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"''আমরা নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81446,"position":3,"arabic":"قَتَلْنَا","translation":"আমরা হত্যা করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81447,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَسِيحَ","translation":"মসীহকে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81448,"position":5,"arabic":"عِيسَى","translation":"(অর্থাৎ) ঈসাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81449,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱبْنَ","translation":"তনয়","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81450,"position":7,"arabic":"مَرْيَمَ","translation":"মারইয়ামের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81451,"position":8,"arabic":"رَسُولَ","translation":"(যিনি) রাসূল","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81452,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর''","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81453,"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81454,"position":11,"arabic":"قَتَلُوهُ","translation":"তাকে তারা হত্যা করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81455,"position":12,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81456,"position":13,"arabic":"صَلَبُوهُ","translation":"তাকে তারা শুলে চড়িয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81457,"position":14,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِن","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81458,"position":15,"arabic":"شُبِّهَ","translation":"বিভ্রম হয়েছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81459,"position":16,"arabic":"لَهُمْ ۚ","translation":"তাদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81461,"position":17,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/004_157_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81462,"position":1